<section id="ErrorResponse" role="topic">
          <title id="ErrorResponse.title">Error Response Elements</title>
          <para>Unless otherwise noted, Amazon Simple Pay returns error information RESTfully as a xml document fragment within the TransactionStatus element. The following table details the elements involved in an error return.</para>
          <para>
               <informaltable>
                    <tgroup cols="2">
                         <?dbhtml table-width="100%" ?>
                         <?dbfo table-width="95%" ?>
                         <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="0.27*"/>
                         <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1.73*"/>
                         <thead>
                              <row>
                                   <entry>Element</entry>
                                   <entry>Description</entry>
                              </row>
                         </thead>
                         <tbody>
                              <row>
                                   <entry>
                                        <para><parameter>Code</parameter></para>
                                   </entry>
                                   <entry>
                                        <para>One of the error codes described previously.</para>
                                        <simpara>Type: String</simpara>
                                   </entry>
                              </row>
                              <row>
                                   <entry>
                                        <para><parameter>Message</parameter></para>
                                   </entry>
                                   <entry>
                                        <para>Human readable description of the error.</para>
                                        <simpara>Type: String</simpara>
                                   </entry>
                              </row>
                              <row>
                                   <entry>
                                        <para><parameter>RequestId</parameter></para>
                                   </entry>
                                   <entry>
                                        <para>Unique identifier for this request. Please provide this to AWS support for debugging purposes.</para>
                                        <simpara>Type: String</simpara>
                                   </entry>
                              </row>
                         </tbody>
                    </tgroup>
               </informaltable>
          </para>
     </section>
